divs: Sighting Detailswe were driving mar 9 2013 ,9pm ,we saw a bright light in sky we stopped it was a orb ,starlike ,bright and it was moving across the sky ,then we noticed 2 others following the same path,then another then 3, all going in same path ,there was about 10 20 not sure we didnt count but there were several.they were moving slow not fast but not real slow ,but all in in line going a straight path .they were in the south heading nw i think ,maybe north ,you could see them moving how to tell how fast ,we video taped it .it was not flashing lights at all ,they were a solid brightness .
